data.description: Highly sought after floor plan that offers wood flooring throughout downstairs except wet areas. TONS of upgrades that have been done to this home. The master bathroom was updated with granite, new sinks, upgraded lighting and brushed chrome cabinet handles. Freshly painted cabinets and shiplap walls with framed mirrors. All interior freshly painted. The kitchen overlooks the living space with granite countertops, new deep mounted sink, fresh white cabinets and added butcher block island. Storage under built in seated breakfast area and all upgraded SS appliances. SOOO much more.
